	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/5a5b701cc84ff4a038900ca46cd0b294?s=49&#038;d=wavatar&#038;r=G' class='avatar avatar-49' height='49' width='49' /><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="https://shenglufashion.com/author/shenglu27/">Sheng Lu</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="https://shenglufashion.com/2020/07/01/ustr-factsheet-textiles-and-apparel-and-the-us-mexico-canada-free-trade-agreement-usmca/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2020-07-01T08:42:00-04:00">July 1, 2020</time><time class="updated" datetime="2020-07-01T09:24:10-04:00">July 1, 2020</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/apparel-industry/" rel="category tag">Apparel industry</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/fash455-course-material/" rel="category tag">FASH455 course material</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/free-trade-agreement-and-trade-preference-program/" rel="category tag">Free trade agreement and trade preference program</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/international-economics-and-trade-theory/" rel="category tag">International economics and trade theory</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/international-trade/" rel="category tag">International Trade</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/tag/sourcing/" rel="category tag">Sourcing</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/statistics/" rel="category tag">Statistics</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/textile-industry/" rel="category tag">Textile industry</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/trade-policy/" rel="category tag">Trade policy</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/usa/" rel="category tag">USA</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/w