	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://shenglufashion.com/2020/06/03/north-american-apparel-market-leaders-talk/" rel="bookmark">North American Apparel Market Leaders&nbsp;Talk</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<div class="jetpack-video-wrapper"><span class="embed-youtube" style="text-align:center; display: block;"><iframe class='youtube-player' width='840' height='473' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/7UNbcpXQJ_w?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent' allowfullscreen='true' style='border:0;'></iframe></span></div>
<p><strong>Panelists:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Julia Hughes, President, United States Fashion Industry Association (USFIA)</li>
<li>Bob Kirke, Executive Director, Canadian Apparel Federation (CAF)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Topics covered:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Textile and apparel trade policy updates</li>
<li>Impact of COVID-19 on the apparel sector and fashion companies&#8217; responses</li>
<li>U.S.-Mexico-Canada  Trade Agreement (USMCA)</li>
<li>Forced labor and related compliance issues</li>
</ul>
