	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/5a5b701cc84ff4a038900ca46cd0b294?s=49&#038;d=wavatar&#038;r=G' class='avatar avatar-49' height='49' width='49' /><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="https://shenglufashion.com/author/shenglu27/">Sheng Lu</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="https://shenglufashion.com/2020/06/03/north-american-apparel-market-leaders-talk/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2020-06-03T08:50:44-04:00">June 3, 2020</time><time class="updated" datetime="2020-06-18T14:46:08-04:00">June 18, 2020</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/apparel-industry/" rel="category tag">Apparel industry</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/fash455-course-material/" rel="category tag">FASH455 course material</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/free-trade-agreement-and-trade-preference-program/" rel="category tag">Free trade agreement and trade preference program</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/tag/sourcing/" rel="category tag">Sourcing</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/trade-policy/" rel="category tag">Trade policy</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/usa/" rel="category tag">USA</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/category/western-hemisphere/" rel="category tag">Western-Hemisphere</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="https://shenglufashion.com/tag/china/" rel="tag">China</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/tag/covid19/" rel="tag">covid19</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/tag/labor/" rel="tag">labor</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/tag/nafta/" rel="tag">NAFTA</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/tag/usmca/" rel="tag">USMCA</a>, <a href="https://shenglufashion.com/tag/western-hemisphere-supply-chain/" rel="tag">western hemisphere supply chain</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="https://shenglufashion.com/2020/06/03/north-american-apparel-market-leaders-talk/#respond">Leave a comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on North American Apparel Market Leaders&nbsp;Talk</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
