str-releases-negotiating-objectives-of-the-proposed-u-s-kenya-free-trade-agreement/#comments">7 Comments<span class="screen-reader-text"> on USTR Releases Negotiating Objectives of the Proposed U.S.-Kenya Free Trade&nbsp;Agreement</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
