<li><a href="https://www.just-style.com/news/timeline-how-coronavirus-is-impacting-the-global-apparel-industry-free-to-read_id138313.aspx">Timeline – How coronavirus is impacting the global apparel industry (Just-Style)</a></li>
</ul>
