	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://shenglufashion.com/2020/01/15/textile-and-apparel-products-covered-by-the-u-s-china-tariff-war-reference-list-updated-december-2019/" rel="bookmark">Textile and Apparel Products Covered by the U.S.-China Tariff War Reference List (updated January&nbsp;2020)</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p><strong>(You may also download this post in <a href="https://shenglufashion.files.wordpress.com/2019/12/us-china-tariff-war-reference-list-jan-15-2020.pdf">PDF</a>)</strong></p><p><a href="https://shenglufashion.files.wordpress.com/2019/12/us-china-tariff-war-reference-list-jan-15-2020_page_1.jpg"><img data-attachment-id="7479" data-permalink="https://shenglufashion.com/2020/01/15/textile-and-apparel-products-covered-by-the-u-s-china-tariff-war-reference-list-updated-december-2019/us-china-tariff-war-reference-list-jan-15-2020_page_1/" data-orig-file="https://shenglufashion.files.wordpress.com/2019/12/us-china-tariff-war-reference-list-jan-15-2020_page_1.jpg" data-orig-size="1289,1434" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="US China tariff war reference list (Jan 15, 2020)_Page_1" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://shenglufashion.files.wordpress.com/2019/12/us-china-tariff-war-reference-list-jan-15-2020_page_1.jpg?w=270" data-large-file="https://shenglufashion.files.wordpress.com/2019/12/us-china-tariff-war-reference-list-jan-15-2020_page_1.jpg?w=1289" class="  wp-image-7479 aligncenter" src="https://shenglufashion.files.wordpress.com/2019/12/us-china-tariff-war-reference-list-jan-15-2020_page_1.jpg" alt="US China tariff war reference list (Jan 15, 2020)_Page_1" width="652" height="726" srcset="https://shenglufashion.files.wordpress.com/2019/12/us-china-tariff-war-reference-list-jan-15-2020_page_1.jpg?w=652&amp;h=726 652w, https://shenglufashion.files.wordpress.com/2019/12/us-china-tariff-war-reference-list-jan-15-2020_page_1.jpg?w=225&amp